{"tid":759720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"張建宗呼籲市民響應捐血行動","createTime":"2018-07-29T01:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T04:24:31.000Z","uid":99493,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"42f694a447aa286bda8b507d42f8ffc1f990e71f","tid":759720,"uid":99493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"政府不時呼籲市民捐血救人，政務司司長張建宗今日（29日）在網誌再度發起呼籲，指血液沒有代用品，儲存期亦有限，需要市民持續捐血，才可為有需要的病人提供足夠的血液進行臨床輸血治療服務，鼓勵政府人員及市民加入捐血行列。<br />\n張建宗以「捐血救人 刻不容緩」為題，指出一包全血已可救治三個或以上病人，並提及在兩星期前政府總部舉行的捐血活動上，聯同食物及衞生局局長陳肇始和多個政策局的局長到場，以示政府對捐血活動的全力支持，活動共有 278 位政府人員參與，成功捐贈204包血液，打破了過往政總捐血日的紀錄。他鼓勵同事積極響應，恆常捐血救人，又期望當在2018-19年度公務員編制預計增加6,700個職位，這些「新血」可加入捐血者行列。<br />\n收集六成血液來自16至40歲人口"},{"pid":"01fb77b4cae06a975cb645e2236a6638c4f53847","tid":759720,"uid":172893,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:41:43.000Z","msg":"捐咗自己啲人工出黎先啦禿頭垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8219927f13f26478b14ed5cb6904dd0045253cdd","tid":759720,"uid":99493,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:42:14.000Z","msg":"捐你老味，有事就叫青年人出嚟 <br />\n你個仆衔政府點樣對待班年青人<br />\n<br />\n777 光頭中 廢柴公務員第一個去捐"},{"pid":"db26bf3aa56b8eb63e6b4242c4051f4ca0f1d9b1","tid":759720,"uid":71655,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:47:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5781e9c7675a4a89bc002823da0f0f42a5060f20","tid":759720,"uid":94828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:48:36.000Z","msg":"不了 我啲廢青血廢事污染你地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"795f70aa33ff4d3919b7eff6afce11e0d48f3458","tid":759720,"uid":33878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:50:03.000Z","msg":"我都呼籲你地政府好多野<br />\n但係政府有無理過？"},{"pid":"1f9779b63626989eaf581cbb19f8151d52047419","tid":759720,"uid":99493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:53:41.000Z","msg":"以前都會去捐<br />\n幫下社會<br />\n<br />\n而家個仆街政府點樣對香港人 <br />\n只要唔犯法<br />\n對社會有好處<br />\n一概不做"},{"pid":"78a6651583ed30bf729e67a14927de553ba0fd5d","tid":759720,"uid":57740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:54:19.000Z","msg":"如果政府肯帶頭<br />\n公務員捐一次血多一日AL<br />\n肯定大把人仆住去捐"},{"pid":"9d10b6372a1abd8719f3981e331aad32512cf386","tid":759720,"uid":179902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:57:13.000Z","msg":"其實應該整個app，可以追蹤返自己包血幾時用、用左係邊間醫院、用左係咩手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54f349c81071b3ac1f7d58b657a75a3bf1a128a5","tid":759720,"uid":99493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T01:59:19.000Z","msg":"西政府同你講幾句<br />\n交功課 <br />\n之後收工返屋企<br />\n<br />\n搵啲偶像明星講效果好好多"},{"pid":"cf638048aed234b680056396ea4de0131aeef67d","tid":759720,"uid":25367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T02:16:52.000Z","msg":"血就大家共享，樓就有錢人霸晒"},{"pid":"ffb4d3ba20bc33670ed209d2cdc44d95695dfa2f","tid":759720,"uid":25367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T02:19:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/090651_2565a15623e1743eb9810a88c4d568af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F090651_2565a15623e1743eb9810a88c4d568af.jpg&h=c7a392c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/090709_6fa38e0a946fc6389ffc15694b15200e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F090709_6fa38e0a946fc6389ffc15694b15200e.jpg&h=ab732a21&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85ef638364f8b9340191af2453721321b922390c","tid":759720,"uid":127123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T02:28:20.000Z","msg":"強制公務員同紀律部隊定